OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly cloudy in the morning
OL,6,Fwith a little drizzle in places, but
OL,7,Fbrighter over Galloway. Dry in the
OL,8,Fafternoon with a few sunny spells
OL,9,Fbreaking through. Becoming very warm
OL,10,Fin the southwest but staying cooler
OL,11,Falong the east coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA bright end to the day then
OL,14,Fremaining dry overnight with long
OL,15,Fclear spells. Becoming rather chilly
OL,16,Fovernight with some patchy mist
OL,17,Fdeveloping.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
