OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FEarly mist soon clearing then
OL,6,Fa dry day with long spells of
OL,7,Fsunshine. Becoming very warm again in
OL,8,Fthe west but cooler towards the east
OL,9,Fcoast.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA dry
OL,12,Ffew days with good spells of sunshine.
OL,13,FWarm in the west with the best of the
OL,14,Fsunshine, cloudier and cooler at times
OL,15,Fin the east.
